#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/image.rst:278
msgid ""
"For those models gguf options are not supported internally, or you want to "
"download gguf files on you own, you can specify additional option "
"``gguf_model_path`` for web UI or spcecify ``--gguf_model_path "
